latitude.description: A measurement datum that is the measure of the latitude coordinate of a site

longitude.description: A measurement datum that is the measure of the longitude coordinate of a site

country.description: A sovereign nation occupying a distinct territory and ruled by an autonomous government.

state.description: An aggregate of governmental organizations that is not itself a sovereign state and whose members are only sovereign states that have some feature in common

field.description: A field  is located on land and can be used for dirrent purposes

name.description: The words or language units by which a thing is known

well.description: A well which has been drilled in order to extract petroleum oil from subterranean reservoirs and bring it to the surface

date.description: The particular day, month and year an event has happened or will happen

startIndex.description: Value of the first index. Unit according to index curve..

endIndex.description: Value of the last index. Unit according to index curve

step.description: Distance between indices if regularly sampled. Unit according to index curve. If log is time based, milliseconds assumed

gammaray.name: GR
gammaray.description: continuous measurement record of naturally occurring gamma rays in the formations adjacent to the wellbore

laterologdeep.name: LLD
laterologdeep.description: continuous measurement record of attenuation resistivity

neutronPorosity.name: NPHI
neutronPorosity.description: continuous measurement record of neutrons emitted concentration in a formation

density.name: RHOB
density.description: continuous measurement record of the bulk density of the formation in a formation

photoelectric.name: PEF
photoelectric.description: continuous measurement record of the  photoelectric absorption factor in a formation

VolumeofClay.name: Vcl
VolumeofClay.description: continuous measurement record of the  volume of clay in a formation

volumeofdolomite.name: VDol
volumeofdolomite.description: continuous measurement record of the  volume of volumes of dolomite in a formation
volumeofdolomite.quantity: formation volumes of dolomite mineral content

volumeofLime.name: VLime
volumeofLime.description: continuous measurement record of the volumes of  limestone in a formation
volumeofLime.quantity: formation volumes of limestone mineral content

volumeofSand.name: VSand
volumeofSand.description: continuous measurement record of the  volumes of  sand in a formation
volumeofSand.quantity: formation volumes of sand mineral content

densityofthemineralMatrix.name: RhoMa
densityofthemineralMatrix.description: continuous measurement record of the matrix density in a formation
densityofthemineralMatrix.quantity: formation volumes of sand mineral content

waterSaturation.name: Sw
waterSaturation.description: continuous measurement record of the water saturation in a formation
waterSaturation.quantity: formation volumes of sand mineral content

porosity.name: PHIE
porosity.description: continuous measurement record of the effective porosity in a formation
porosity.quantity: formation volumes of sand mineral content

totalPorosity.name: PHIT
totalPorosity.description: continuous measurement record of the total porosity of clean (clay free) sand  in a formation
totalPorosity.quantity: formation volumes of sand mineral content

totalorganicCarbon.name: TOC
totalorganicCarbon.description: continuous measurement record of the weight percent of total organic matter content in a formation
totalorganicCarbon.quantity: formation percentage of organic matter content

rockType.name: Rock_type
rockType.description: continuous measurement record of the rock type in a formation
